text: Over-65s can now book their #Covid19 #vaccine at the BIC, Bournemouth. Anyone who has had a letter inviting them for the #jab can book direct, using their NHS number, on the national booking system – https://t.co/ysFRmX3xRD – or by ringing 119 if they don’t have internet access. https://t.co/IQ8ZgqvCGS
